@startuml ACR-QA-Pipeline-Stages
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
'  ACR-QA  v5.0.0rc2  —  12-Stage Processing Pipeline
'  Portrait A4 — NO scale, activity diagram, fontSize 11
'  King Salman International University · CSE494 · 2025-26
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName  "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize  11
skinparam shadowing        false

skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor        #E8EDF4
  BorderColor            #002654
  BorderThickness        2
  FontSize               11
  DiamondBackgroundColor #FFF3BF
  DiamondBorderColor     #C9A84C
  DiamondFontSize        10
}

skinparam arrow {
  Color     #002654
  FontColor #444444
  FontSize  10
  Thickness 1.5
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor     #C9A84C
  FontSize        10
}

start

:⓪  **Rate Limit & Job Init**
Redis token-bucket check · POST /v1/runs → 202 Accepted
Celery task enqueued · run ID returned;

:①  **Repository Ingestion**
Validate path · detect languages (.py / .ts / .go)
PostgreSQL: status = RUNNING;

fork
  :Python
  Ruff · Bandit · Semgrep
  Vulture · Radon · SCA;
fork again
  :JavaScript / TS
  ESLint · Semgrep
  npm audit · jscpd;
fork again
  :Go
  gosec · staticcheck
  Semgrep;
fork again
  :All Languages
  Secrets Detector
  IaC Scanner (28 rules);
end fork

note right
  ②  12 tools in parallel
  thread pool · 300 s timeout
  tool failures silently skipped
end note

:③a  **Normalise → CanonicalFinding**
Map all tool output to canonical schema (file / line / severity);

:③b–c  **Triage Memory & Cross-Tool Deduplication**
Suppress known FPs · merge overlapping findings;

:③d  **Intra-Procedural Taint Analysis**
AST BFS: HTTP sources → dangerous sinks
Cs_taint = max(0.4, 0.95 − 0.1 × hop_count);

:③e  **Call-Graph Reachability  (BFS, max_depth=5)**
Entry points: Flask/FastAPI routes · Celery tasks · __main__;

if (finding reachable?) then (yes)
else (no — dead code)
  :Apply −20 confidence penalty
  (retained for audit, ranked last);
endif

:③f  **Cap (5 per rule) & Sort by Cs descending;**

:④  **Five-Signal Confidence Scoring**
severity(40%) · category(20%) · tool_reliability(15%)
rule_specificity(10%) · fix_validation(10%)  →  Cs ∈ [0, 100];

:⑤  **RAG Enrichment**
dict_lookup(rule_id) O(1) · Groq LLaMA-3.3-70B × 3 runs
N-gram entropy filter τ = 3.2 bits · 100% enrichment rate;

note right
  96.0% pass entropy filter
  2,407 / 2,508 API calls accepted
end note

:⑤b  **LLM-Augmented Detection & Second Opinion**
LLMDetector gated at 0.75 · Ollama qwen2.5-coder:1.5b
+5.2 pp recall gain · ±15 / −10 confidence adjustment;

:⑤c  **Post-Quantum Attestation**
ECDSA-P256 (classical) + CRYSTALS-Dilithium3 (NIST FIPS 204);

:⑥  **Supply Chain SCA & CBoM**
pip-audit / npm audit (OSV offline ~1.5 GB)
CBoM: 62 cryptographic algorithms · PQC-deprecated flagging;

:⑦  **Quality Gate  (.acrqa.yml)**
FAIL: CRITICAL Cs≥70 · >5 HIGH findings · any secret Cs≥50;

:⑧  **Output Delivery**
JSON · SARIF 2.1 · HTML · PDF
PostgreSQL persist · GitHub PR inline comments;

stop

@enduml
